OL,3,CJustice Secretary to set out reforms
OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,FPlans to free up crown courts to deal
OL,7,Fwith serious crimes swiftly and hand
OL,8,Fmore support to victims are set to be
OL,9,Fannounced by the Justice Secretary as
OL,10,Fpart of efforts to tackle the "courts
OL,11,Femergency".
OL,13,FDavid Lammy, who is also Deputy Prime
OL,14,FMinister, will lay out reforms to
OL,15,Foverhaul the system on Tuesday, amid
OL,16,Freports jury trials could be limited
OL,17,Fto the most serious offences such as
OL,18,Frape and murder.
