OL,3,CJustice Secretary to set out reforms
OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,FThe move to give victims the "swift
OL,7,Fjustice they deserve" comes amid a
OL,8,Frecord-high backlog of crown court
OL,9,Fcases totalling more than 78,000, and
OL,10,Ftrials listed as far as 2030.
OL,12,FMinisters have warned the backlog
OL,13,Fcould rise to 100,000 by 2028 if
OL,14,Fnothing is done, with a growing number
OL,15,Fof victims giving up on seeking
OL,16,Fjustice because of the lengthy delays.
OL,26,@nD@^OUoD@UO]
