OL,3,CJustice Secretary to set out reforms
OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,FMr Lammy said: "Today I am calling
OL,7,Ftime on the courts emergency that has
OL,8,Fleft victims of the most serious
OL,9,Fcrimes waiting years for justice and
OL,10,Fpushed the justice system to the brink
OL,11,Fof collapse.
OL,13,F"For many victims, justice delayed is
OL,14,Foften justice denied.
OL,16,F"Some give up on the process, while
OL,17,Fothers have no confidence justice will
OL,18,Fbe served if they report a crime, and
OL,19,Fperpetrators never held to account.
OL,26,@nD@POUuD@AOUxD@AOU
