OL,6,F"This simply cannot go on ` we must be
OL,7,Fbold.
OL,9,F"I will set out a fast and fair
OL,10,Fjustice plan that gives victims and
OL,11,Fsurvivors the swift justice they
OL,12,Fdeserve."
