OL,3,CJustice Secretary to set out reforms
OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,FMr Lammy will reveal the Government's
OL,7,Fresponse to recommendations made by
OL,8,FSir Brian Leveson in July to reform
OL,9,Fthe courts system and tackle the
OL,10,Fbacklog, which include diverting more
OL,11,Foffences to magistrates' courts or to
OL,12,Fa new intermediate court where a judge
OL,13,Fwould hear cases with two lay
OL,14,Fmagistrates.
OL,16,FThe former senior judge called for
OL,17,Fjuries to be reserved to hear the most
OL,18,Fserious cases, of "indictable-only"
OL,19,Fsuch as murder, rape and manslaughter,
OL,20,Fand lesser "either way" offences when
OL,21,Fa judge deems it appropriate.
