OL,3,CJustice Secretary to set out reforms
OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,FHe said: "This is about saving the
OL,7,Fjury system."
OL,9,FThe Justice Secretary is expected to
OL,10,Fset out plans to boost control for
OL,11,Fjudges on how to handle cases, and
OL,12,Fcreate faster routes for lower-level
OL,13,Fcases like in Canada, which has judge-
OL,14,Fonly trials and where courts minister
OL,15,FSarah Sackman KC visited last month.
