OL,3,CJustice Secretary to set out reforms
OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,FProposals to curb jury trials have
OL,7,Ffaced opposition from MPs and legal
OL,8,Fprofessionals, including from the
OL,9,FCriminal Bar Association and the Bar
OL,10,FCouncil, which argued "there is no
OL,11,Fneed to curtail the right to a trial
OL,12,Fby jury ` from both a principle and
OL,13,Fpractical position".
