OL,3,CJustice Secretary to set out reforms
OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,FReports of Mr Lammy considering
OL,7,Frestricting jury trials further than
OL,8,FSir Brian's recommendations have also
OL,9,Ffaced backlash as an "extreme measure"
OL,10,Fby the Law Society of England and
OL,11,FWales, which has not seen any "real
OL,12,Fevidence" it will work to reduce the
OL,13,Fbacklog.
OL,15,FShadow justice secretary Robert
OL,16,FJenrick accused Mr Lammy of abandoning
OL,17,Fhis principles while in Government
OL,18,Fhaving previously defended juries.
