OL,3,CJustice Secretary to set out reforms
OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,F"This year alone 21,000 court sitting
OL,7,Fdays have been missed and the court
OL,8,Fbacklog is up 10% on their watch," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"Instead of depriving British citizens
OL,12,Fof ancient liberties, David Lammy
OL,13,Fshould get his own department in
OL,14,Forder."
OL,16,FAccording to the Ministry of Justice
OL,17,F(MoJ) nearly half of the cases in the
OL,18,Fbacklog are over violent and sexual
OL,19,Foffences, and only about 3% of
OL,20,Fcriminal cases are currently heard
OL,21,Fwith a judge and a jury.
