OL,3,CJustice Secretary to set out reforms
OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,FAs part of the announcement, #550
OL,7,Fmillion will also be given to victim
OL,8,Fsupport services over the next three
OL,9,Fyears to help survivors and witnesses
OL,10,Fthrough the justice process, such as
OL,11,Fthrough counselling and advice on
OL,12,Fattending court.
OL,14,FThe late victims' commissioner
OL,15,FBaroness Helen Newlove had repeatedly
OL,16,Fraised concerns over victims'
OL,17,Fservices, and said in October that
OL,18,F"support can be the difference between
OL,19,Fa victim staying engaged or walking
OL,20,Faway from the justice process".
