OL,3,CJustice Secretary to set out reforms
OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,FAn annual survey of victims by the
OL,7,Fwatchdog found less than half of
OL,8,Frespondents were confident the
OL,9,Fcriminal justice system is effective
OL,10,For that they could get justice by
OL,11,Freporting a crime.
OL,13,FIncoming victims' commissioner Claire
OL,14,FWaxman, who will take up the role in
OL,15,Fthe new year, welcomed the MoJ funding
OL,16,Fas a "necessary step", but added: "The
OL,17,Fsums pledged are not a silver bullet
OL,18,Ffor the wider crisis facing the
OL,19,Fsector."
