OL,6,F"Ultimately, these services are
OL,7,Fcrucial to a victim's recovery ` and
OL,8,Fthey will be just as essential to the
OL,9,Frecovery of the justice system as a
OL,10,Fwhole," she said.
OL,12,FFormer Law Society president Richard
OL,13,FAtkinson said the extra funding was
OL,14,Fwelcome but "only papers over the
OL,15,Fcracks and doesn't address the
OL,16,Ffundamental problems".
