OL,3,CJustice Secretary to set out reforms
OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,FElsewhere, Mr Lammy has committed to
OL,7,Fmore sitting days in the crown court
OL,8,Fon top of a record number to help
OL,9,Fclear the backlog and a match-fund
OL,10,Fscheme to support more young people to
OL,11,Fbegin their careers as criminal
OL,12,Fbarristers.
OL,14,FAhead of the full details for reform,
OL,15,FMagistrates' Association chief
OL,16,Fexecutive Tom Franklin said measures
OL,17,Fthat can speed up justice for victims,
OL,18,Fwitnesses and defendants are "worth
OL,19,Fconsidering ` as long as they balance
OL,20,Fthe efficiency with quality of
OL,21,Fjustice".
