OL,4,Cto tackle 'courts emergency'
OL,6,FHe said the independent body will be
OL,7,Flooking for more details on how
OL,8,Fchanges will be brought for
OL,9,Fmagistrates' courts in Tuesday's
OL,10,Fannouncement, adding: "To bring down
OL,11,Fthe huge backlog in the crown courts,
OL,12,Fall parts of the courts system need to
OL,13,Fbe resourced and supported, including
OL,14,Fthe magistrates' courts, which barely
OL,15,Fmerit a mention in this morning's
OL,16,Fannouncement."
